{"tid":2305999,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"卡雲尼建功向好友蘇亞雷斯致敬","createTime":"2020-11-30T06:26:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T12:29:23.000Z","uid":253829,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"195351d73ea5b939bb05c5aee86c2a50f8b57a76","tid":2305999,"uid":253829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T06:26:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/59TOXdEV932Cwqx_ykjXwig_GpQ=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/J7M4TKE5QZBRFLWBAU7WXHR2J4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F59TOXdEV932Cwqx_ykjXwig_GpQ%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJ7M4TKE5QZBRFLWBAU7WXHR2J4.jpg&h=896d3663&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早於2011年10月利物浦對曼聯的賽事中，卡雲尼的國家隊好拍檔蘇亞雷斯，曾用上同樣的單詞「Negrito」（黑人）來稱呼曼聯後衞艾拉，雖然當時蘇亞雷斯解釋這個詞語，在烏拉圭及拉丁美洲地區沒有冒犯性，但仍被英足總重罰停賽8場及罰款4萬鎊。事後蘇亞雷斯曾在自傳中解釋：「Negro可以指任何黑頭髮或黑皮膚的人，我一生人講西班牙語時都有用這個詞語，有時候妻子會稱呼我Negro或Negrito，我的祖父亦會這樣稱呼祖母。」不過英國或英足總方面，似乎仍不接受這種解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/1459649.main_image.jpg?strip=all\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F04%2F1459649.main_image.jpg%3Fstrip%3Dall&h=a5d463f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29e12228ee875d69679f8f2bb4cc5a04709afd25","tid":2305999,"uid":253715,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T06:28:04.000Z","msg":"同而家美國人唔比人講black一樣，話你黑都已經係歧視，一定係「非裔」，反智到"},{"pid":"e3edc9a0967acbbebb3155c926d794f8ac0aa111","tid":2305999,"uid":342115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T06:34:39.000Z","msg":"Negrito 係矮黑人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 南亞有個人種係叫Negrito <br />\n唔係乜春都關非洲事嘅"},{"pid":"2d6e8b1835e82ee68da8e94459f2e5a50fa38204","tid":2305999,"uid":342115,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pi